3
00:01:35,370 --> 00:01:37,630
[Episode 22]

4
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:41,530
You normally

5
00:01:41,580 --> 00:01:42,780
talk quite a lot

6
00:01:43,340 --> 00:01:44,270
with Lu Yanchen.

7
00:01:45,220 --> 00:01:47,150
We've known each other for so long.

8
00:01:47,580 --> 00:01:48,860
When men come together,

9
00:01:48,860 --> 00:01:49,789
we talk more.

10
00:01:49,900 --> 00:01:51,100
I don't know

11
00:01:51,630 --> 00:01:53,289
what to talk about with a girl.

12
00:01:53,700 --> 00:01:55,200
Are you tired?

13
00:01:55,380 --> 00:01:55,780
No.

14
00:01:57,800 --> 00:01:58,750
Show me around.

15
00:01:59,400 --> 00:01:59,870
Sure.

16
00:01:59,900 --> 00:02:02,300
Where do you want to go? I'll take you there.

17
00:02:04,780 --> 00:02:06,660
Is Qining close?

18
00:02:07,340 --> 00:02:09,660
Yes, very close, it's just half an hour away.

19
00:02:09,660 --> 00:02:10,060
Great.

20
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:23,530
If we go further down, we'll enter Qining.

21
00:02:24,310 --> 00:02:26,630
When I first came here

22
00:02:26,860 --> 00:02:27,980
to report,

23
00:02:28,890 --> 00:02:31,620
I stood on the prairie and watched for a long time.

24
00:02:34,260 --> 00:02:35,440
It's indeed a scenery

25
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:36,840
you can't see in Beijing.

26
00:02:36,980 --> 00:02:37,350
Yes.

27
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:39,880
When we get to a place with a broader view,

28
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:42,010
let's go down and I'll show you around.

29
00:02:46,270 --> 00:02:47,710
As for things like malls,

30
00:02:48,500 --> 00:02:49,560
since you're here,

31
00:02:49,850 --> 00:02:51,530
I don't think you'd be interested to see them, right?

32
00:02:51,530 --> 00:02:52,590
No shopping malls.

33
00:02:53,380 --> 00:02:55,840
I just want to see the scenery of our country.

34
00:02:55,900 --> 00:02:57,430
Okay, I'll show them to you.

35
00:03:16,660 --> 00:03:18,120
Do you want to ride a camel?

36
00:03:18,579 --> 00:03:19,200
Is there?

37
00:03:19,700 --> 00:03:20,960
There are some nearby.

38
00:03:21,010 --> 00:03:22,470
Tourists would rent them.

39
00:03:22,790 --> 00:03:23,650
I'll go get two.

40
00:03:23,940 --> 00:03:25,340
I will ride one by myself?

41
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:26,490
I don't know how.

42
00:03:27,020 --> 00:03:27,579
Well...

43
00:03:28,220 --> 00:03:29,150
It's not too good

44
00:03:29,850 --> 00:03:31,380
for the two of us to ride one.

45
00:03:31,410 --> 00:03:33,410
I'm not saying I'd ride one with you,

46
00:03:33,740 --> 00:03:34,870
but that

47
00:03:35,660 --> 00:03:38,090
I'd learn, and would need you to help hold the camel.

48
00:03:38,090 --> 00:03:39,090
Sure, no problem.

49
00:03:39,540 --> 00:03:40,260
Wait here.

50
00:03:40,460 --> 00:03:41,320
I'll go get one.

51
00:03:46,829 --> 00:03:48,090
He's just like his son.

52
00:04:01,770 --> 00:04:02,580
Captain Qin.

53
00:04:03,260 --> 00:04:04,520
Will you help me or not?

54
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:05,720
Of course.

55
00:04:06,420 --> 00:04:07,300
Well,

56
00:04:07,500 --> 00:04:09,360
I'm afraid I might cross the line.

57
00:04:10,140 --> 00:04:10,980
Captain Qin,

58
00:04:11,540 --> 00:04:14,400
you don't look like someone who had married before.

59
00:04:14,770 --> 00:04:15,810
A wife is a wife.

60
00:04:16,050 --> 00:04:17,230
You are a girl,

61
00:04:17,310 --> 00:04:20,180
of course I should be more careful as to how I treat you.

62
00:04:20,180 --> 00:04:20,839
How feudal.

63
00:04:21,459 --> 00:04:22,060
Come here.

64
00:04:27,540 --> 00:04:28,140
Sit tight.

65
00:04:34,900 --> 00:04:35,860
You look better

66
00:04:36,260 --> 00:04:36,990
on the camel.

67
00:04:39,100 --> 00:04:39,820
I'll hold it

68
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:40,780
and let it walk.

69
00:04:40,950 --> 00:04:41,280
Okay.

70
00:04:47,030 --> 00:04:48,140
Before I came to Qining,

71
00:04:48,140 --> 00:04:49,870
I've never rode a camel before.

72
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:50,460
I learned even horseriding

73
00:04:50,460 --> 00:04:51,720
only after I came here.

74
00:04:52,380 --> 00:04:53,710
After I have stayed here

75
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:54,659
for a long time,

76
00:04:55,390 --> 00:04:57,110
I gradually became like Captain Lu,

77
00:04:57,110 --> 00:04:57,850
and now take this

78
00:04:57,850 --> 00:04:59,110
as my second hometown.

79
00:04:59,940 --> 00:05:01,140
Anywhere on our great

80
00:05:01,290 --> 00:05:02,890
motherland is our hometown.

81
00:05:03,250 --> 00:05:04,710
It's the same everywhere.

82
00:05:05,490 --> 00:05:06,350
I didn't expect

83
00:05:06,370 --> 00:05:08,350
you to have such a broad outlook in life.

84
00:05:08,350 --> 00:05:09,280
What do you mean?

85
00:05:11,650 --> 00:05:12,690
When I was young,

86
00:05:12,970 --> 00:05:13,970
there was a flood.

87
00:05:14,880 --> 00:05:15,790
There were many people

88
00:05:15,790 --> 00:05:17,280
who came to help from everywhere.

89
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:18,780
So when it comes to crucial times,

90
00:05:18,780 --> 00:05:19,780
it's all the same.

91
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:21,850
Every province is the same.

92
00:05:22,630 --> 00:05:23,890
The only difference is

93
00:05:25,260 --> 00:05:26,790
the difference in scenery.

94
00:05:47,180 --> 00:05:48,380
They are indeed here.

95
00:05:49,909 --> 00:05:50,870
Qin Mingyu

96
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:52,530
knows nothing but work,

97
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:53,780
and has no life.

98
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:56,400
If I get him to bring a girl around,

99
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:57,930
good chance he'd bring them

100
00:05:58,220 --> 00:05:58,580
here.

101
00:06:01,670 --> 00:06:02,330
Qin Mingyu.

102
00:06:05,050 --> 00:06:05,930
You're here.

103
00:06:06,370 --> 00:06:07,740
Do you want to ride a camel?

104
00:06:07,740 --> 00:06:08,470
You go ahead.

105
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:10,040
Don't worry about us.

106
00:06:13,510 --> 00:06:14,710
You can't ride it now.

107
00:06:14,940 --> 00:06:15,540
Next time.

108
00:06:16,100 --> 00:06:16,850
Got it.

109
00:06:23,060 --> 00:06:25,040
You really don't treat me as an outsider?

110
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,000
I'm just...

111
00:06:26,650 --> 00:06:27,710
What are you doing?

112
00:06:30,300 --> 00:06:32,270
Business has not been good these days.

113
00:06:32,270 --> 00:06:33,710
I have to drink with

114
00:06:33,740 --> 00:06:34,940
those bosses at night.

115
00:06:34,940 --> 00:06:35,970
He's a child.

116
00:06:36,500 --> 00:06:37,700
It's not convenient.

117
00:06:39,100 --> 00:06:39,700
All right.

118
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,920
Leave the kid with me.

119
00:06:41,700 --> 00:06:43,300
You're the best in the world.

120
00:06:44,010 --> 00:06:44,730
Stop.

121
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,370
I'm married.

122
00:06:46,420 --> 00:06:47,760
I know, I know.

123
00:06:48,300 --> 00:06:50,100
I wouldn't dare to mess with Qin.

124
00:06:51,890 --> 00:06:52,330
Qin.

125
00:06:53,780 --> 00:06:54,880
I'm leaving then.

126
00:06:55,780 --> 00:06:56,260
Bye.

127
00:06:56,980 --> 00:06:57,510
Xiaonan.

128
00:06:57,650 --> 00:06:58,850
Call me if anything happens.

129
00:06:58,850 --> 00:06:59,650
Keep in touch.

130
00:07:05,330 --> 00:07:06,390
Did you notice that

131
00:07:06,910 --> 00:07:07,970
he's afraid of you?

132
00:07:08,630 --> 00:07:09,510
He's not.

133
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,950
He's a good person.

134
00:07:12,490 --> 00:07:13,950
He's avoiding suspicion.

135
00:07:14,110 --> 00:07:15,620
You're still defending him?

136
00:07:15,620 --> 00:07:16,410
It's rare.

137
00:07:17,410 --> 00:07:18,840
I quite like him.

138
00:07:19,460 --> 00:07:20,380
In the past few days,

139
00:07:20,380 --> 00:07:21,760
some old friends

140
00:07:21,790 --> 00:07:22,290
asked me

141
00:07:22,620 --> 00:07:24,280
if he's reliable to work with.

142
00:07:24,430 --> 00:07:25,390
I said of course.

143
00:07:26,470 --> 00:07:27,540
Stop talking about adult things.

144
00:07:27,540 --> 00:07:28,740
There's a child here.

145
00:07:30,230 --> 00:07:31,610
We don't have children either.

146
00:07:31,610 --> 00:07:33,610
Why don't you try taking care of him?

147
00:07:37,620 --> 00:07:38,260
I'll try?

148
00:07:41,250 --> 00:07:42,560
Hello, I'm Qin Feng.

149
00:07:43,380 --> 00:07:44,130
Hello, Uncle.

150
00:07:44,130 --> 00:07:45,390
My name is Qin Xiaonan.

151
00:07:45,850 --> 00:07:46,210
Good.

152
00:07:47,580 --> 00:07:48,420
We are all

153
00:07:48,990 --> 00:07:49,900
Aunt Gui Xiao,

154
00:07:49,930 --> 00:07:51,790
and Uncle Lu Chen's good friends.

155
00:07:52,290 --> 00:07:53,620
When you are in Beijing,

156
00:07:53,659 --> 00:07:56,780
it's inevitable that we might take turns to take care of you.

157
00:07:56,780 --> 00:07:58,200
You see, with more parents

158
00:07:58,200 --> 00:07:59,110
taking care of you,

159
00:07:59,110 --> 00:07:59,800
and bringing you out to play,

160
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,420
it is quite a good deal too.

161
00:08:00,420 --> 00:08:00,860
Right?

162
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,470
He's so tough.

163
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,490
Duan Rou was not sleepy.

164
00:08:11,510 --> 00:08:12,970
I have nowhere to take her.

165
00:08:13,260 --> 00:08:13,660
Yes.

166
00:08:13,690 --> 00:08:15,470
I was the one who wanted to come here.

167
00:08:15,470 --> 00:08:16,110
Are there

168
00:08:16,140 --> 00:08:17,670
better places suitable for

169
00:08:18,470 --> 00:08:21,000
Lu Chen and I to strengthen our relationship?

170
00:08:21,550 --> 00:08:22,590
Of course.

171
00:08:22,830 --> 00:08:23,630
Take us there.

172
00:08:24,540 --> 00:08:25,760
Yes, take us there.

173
00:08:26,020 --> 00:08:27,180
But it's a bit far.

174
00:08:28,660 --> 00:08:29,990
Take your time to drive.

175
00:08:31,220 --> 00:08:31,580
Okay.

176
00:08:34,610 --> 00:08:35,210
All right.

177
00:08:35,340 --> 00:08:36,470
You can't even talk.

178
00:08:36,510 --> 00:08:37,840
We'll take the same car.

179
00:08:50,860 --> 00:08:53,100
You talked to me about her before she came.

180
00:08:53,100 --> 00:08:54,230
Now that she's here,

181
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,370
you're all so timid.

182
00:08:56,180 --> 00:08:56,870
I'm not.

183
00:08:56,970 --> 00:08:58,180
I'm just afraid that

184
00:08:58,290 --> 00:09:00,110
I will be a bad host to Gui Xiao's friend.

185
00:09:00,110 --> 00:09:01,070
She's been taking care of Xiaonan for you

186
00:09:01,070 --> 00:09:01,730
for so long.

187
00:09:02,140 --> 00:09:04,140
She's just Gui Xiao's friend to you?

188
00:09:04,580 --> 00:09:05,180
Of course.

189
00:09:06,060 --> 00:09:07,520
Where's your conscience?

190
00:09:09,620 --> 00:09:10,020
Fine.

191
00:09:10,990 --> 00:09:12,370
I kind of like her, but

192
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,970
I don't think I deserve her.

193
00:09:22,740 --> 00:09:24,380
You're usually all cool.

194
00:09:24,410 --> 00:09:26,430
Why are you so quiet now?

195
00:09:28,220 --> 00:09:28,880
What?

196
00:09:32,130 --> 00:09:32,930
Actually,

197
00:09:33,820 --> 00:09:34,500
I’m here

198
00:09:35,330 --> 00:09:37,010
to firstly see Lu Chen.

199
00:09:38,230 --> 00:09:38,910
Secondly,

200
00:09:39,680 --> 00:09:40,710
I want you to formally

201
00:09:40,710 --> 00:09:41,760
meet Qin Mingyu.

202
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:44,490
I see.

203
00:09:47,070 --> 00:09:49,120
I just haven't decided.

204
00:09:50,860 --> 00:09:52,170
It looks like...

205
00:09:52,910 --> 00:09:53,740
he's not too interested

206
00:09:53,740 --> 00:09:54,740
in me.

207
00:09:55,620 --> 00:09:57,150
When I was riding the camel,

208
00:09:57,690 --> 00:09:59,550
he didn't want to help me get on it.

209
00:10:01,940 --> 00:10:03,400
But I don't think that way.

210
00:10:03,910 --> 00:10:05,420
I think he's

211
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:06,840
quite interested in you.

212
00:10:09,050 --> 00:10:09,620
Really?

213
00:10:11,970 --> 00:10:13,170
Lu Chen thinks so too.

214
00:10:13,880 --> 00:10:15,050
He knows Qin Mingyu.

215
00:10:29,980 --> 00:10:30,840
[Meili Valley]

216
00:10:48,470 --> 00:10:49,330
So beautiful.

217
00:11:02,270 --> 00:11:03,470
Take care of Duan Rou.

218
00:11:03,540 --> 00:11:04,870
I'll look after my wife.

219
00:11:05,860 --> 00:11:06,190
Okay.

220
00:11:19,420 --> 00:11:20,350
Look over there.

221
00:11:34,250 --> 00:11:35,250
It's a bit high up.

222
00:11:35,310 --> 00:11:36,240
Don't be afraid.

223
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:37,130
Let's go.

224
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:39,250
I'm here.

225
00:11:41,590 --> 00:11:42,270
Wait, wait.

226
00:11:42,300 --> 00:11:43,630
Let me tie my hair first.

227
00:11:59,770 --> 00:12:00,500
Oh my god.

