264
00:13:38,140 --> 00:13:41,720
[Line A starting point]

265
00:13:41,860 --> 00:13:43,380
Hello, welcome.

266
00:13:43,380 --> 00:13:43,780
Hello.

267
00:14:09,070 --> 00:14:10,660
Let's go back.

268
00:14:11,790 --> 00:14:13,130
I'm here. Go ahead.

269
00:14:14,310 --> 00:14:14,770
Come on.

270
00:14:27,880 --> 00:14:28,680
Look forward.

271
00:14:30,610 --> 00:14:31,210
I'm fine.

272
00:14:31,760 --> 00:14:32,690
Steady, steady.

273
00:14:32,940 --> 00:14:33,670
Step by step.

274
00:14:34,580 --> 00:14:34,910
Go.

275
00:14:55,950 --> 00:14:56,580
Look.

276
00:14:58,100 --> 00:14:58,630
Duan Rou.

277
00:15:02,180 --> 00:15:02,940
This is the first time

278
00:15:02,940 --> 00:15:04,470
Qin Mingyu is on the bridge.

279
00:15:04,540 --> 00:15:05,760
He refused to do it before.

280
00:15:05,760 --> 00:15:06,860
He thought it was not sturdy.

281
00:15:06,860 --> 00:15:07,460
Really?

282
00:15:08,220 --> 00:15:09,680
It's to make him look good.

283
00:15:13,100 --> 00:15:14,360
Is what Captain Lu said

284
00:15:14,800 --> 00:15:15,590
true?

285
00:15:15,620 --> 00:15:16,210
No.

286
00:15:16,740 --> 00:15:17,740
I came here often.

287
00:15:18,220 --> 00:15:19,030
There was once

288
00:15:19,060 --> 00:15:19,980
I even brought Xiaonan

289
00:15:19,980 --> 00:15:21,780
to cross from here to over there.

290
00:15:22,580 --> 00:15:23,200
Then...

291
00:15:23,710 --> 00:15:26,040
Why did he say this is your first time here?

292
00:15:27,130 --> 00:15:27,900
Maybe it's to

293
00:15:27,900 --> 00:15:29,500
